## Phase 7: Install Monitoring Stack

### 7.1 — Deploy Prometheus + Grafana + Tempo + OTEL
```bash
cd ~/cd-repo/apps/monitoring
helm dependency update .

helm upgrade --install monitoring . \
  --namespace monitoring \
  --timeout 10m \
  --wait

kubectl get pods -n monitoring
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Prometheus, Grafana, Tempo, OTEL Collector pods running

### 7.2 — Access Grafana
```bash
# Get Grafana URL via port-forward (from bastion)
kubectl port-forward svc/prometheus-grafana -n monitoring 3000:80 &
echo "Grafana: http://localhost:3000"
echo "Username: admin"
echo "Password: admin"
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Grafana login + "API Overview — SU DevOps" dashboard

