### 8.1 — Deploy Loki + Promtail
```bash
cd ~/cd-repo/apps/logging
helm dependency update .

helm upgrade --install logging . \
  --namespace logging \
  --timeout 5m \
  --wait

kubectl get pods -n logging
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Loki and Promtail pods running

### 8.2 — Verify Logs
```bash
# Check Promtail is shipping logs
kubectl logs -n logging -l app.kubernetes.io/name=promtail --tail=5
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Promtail log shipping active

