## Phase 9: Apply Network Policies

### 9.1 — Apply All Policies
```bash
kubectl apply -f ~/cd-repo/network-policies/
kubectl get networkpolicies -A
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Network policies in all namespaces

### 9.2 — Verify Policy Details
```bash
echo "=== Default Deny Policies ==="
kubectl get networkpolicies -A | grep default-deny
echo ""
echo "=== Allow Rules ==="
kubectl get networkpolicies -A | grep allow
```
📸 **Screenshot**: Default-deny + explicit allow rules

